{
  "stem": "5357.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she took me in, as poor as she was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She told her two children that went to school, don't you dare say that we keep Dorka here, because I'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whoever-- she had a latch, not a key, that you latch door.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when somebody knocked on the door, because it was locked like this, she kept it open, I had to go under the bed, because they didn't even have a cupboard to go into.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I stayed there through the winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After the winter, she said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't keep you anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where am I going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to Karczew, where my sister and her husband and my brother were hidden.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I knew the farmers too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I waited 'til the night, because you couldn't go at daytime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No neighbors should see you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was in the garden 'til it got dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I walked up to see nobody sees me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she opened the door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I have to see my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not staying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I just have to ask her what I should do next.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she led me down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a cellar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he dug a hole to go down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there was another hole to go up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he covered that part, so if somebody comes to the cellar, they don't see anything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was a dark, really hole, that was like a half a-- a flat brick, like this one, the bigger one.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all for the air.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They weren't allowed to talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They weren't allowed to burn a candle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had just to be there quiet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very small and low.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
